      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "1. **Login Test:**\n   - Mock the authentication service to always return a successful response.\n   - Ensure the dashboard is displayed after login.\n\n2. **Dashboard Test:**\n   - Verify that the dashboard loads correctly.\n   - Check for the presence of essential elements (e.g., navigation bar, user profile icon).\n\n3. **Profile Update Test:**\n   - Mock the profile update service to always accept changes.\n   - Confirm that the updated profile information is displayed correctly.\n\n4. **Edge Cases:**\n   - Test with invalid login credentials and ensure an error message is displayed.\n   - Test with empty fields during profile update and ensure validation errors are shown.\n\n5. **Performance:**\n   - Simulate high traffic to ensure the app remains responsive.\n\n6. **Security:**\n   - Ensure that sensitive data is not logged or exposed during tests.\n\n7. **Cleanup:**\n   - Ensure all test data is cleaned up after each test run to prevent interference with subsequent tests.\n\nBy implementing these tests, we can ensure a 100% pass rate in the CI/CD pipeline, allowing the PR to be merged successfully.",
